OL,3,CCommunity event raises awareness about
OL,4,Chidden disabilities in Guernsey
OL,6,FA community event to promote the
OL,7,FSunflower Hidden Disabilities Scheme
OL,8,Fwas held at Beau Sejour, on Saturday 6
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FAn estimated 13,500 islanders in live
OL,12,Fwith disabilities, with about 80% of
OL,13,Fthese are hidden disabilities, such as
OL,14,Fneurological disorders or visual
OL,15,Fimpairments.
OL,17,FThe scheme allows islanders to
OL,18,Fvoluntarily share that they have a
OL,19,Fdisability or condition that may not
OL,20,Fbe immediately apparent, through
OL,21,Fwearing a sunflower lanyard.
