OL,6,FThese lanyards indicate that the
OL,7,Fwearer they may need a helping hand,
OL,8,Funderstanding, or more time such as in
OL,9,Fpublic spaces, shops or at work.
OL,11,FDisability Officer, Gill Evans said:
OL,12,F"At the end of the day it's about
OL,13,Fbeing inclusive but it's also about
OL,14,Fbeing kind and about being a little
OL,15,Fbit patient - sometimes it's about
OL,16,Fgiving that person a little more time."
